Ex. 2: Design a basic HTML page layout for a blog post. Create a structure that includes the following elements:
	A header section with the blog post title.
	A navigation bar with links for "Home," "About," "Blog," and "Contact."
	A main content area with the blog post content, including a title, author's name, publication date, and text.
	A sidebar on the right side with a list of recent posts.
